    "rich_text_PJEcwj": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_Pxqnkn": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Why We Exist",
            "title_highlight_color": "#6d388b",
            "heading_size": "h1"
          }
        },
        "text_KVyEqE": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>At Patriot 250th, we believe the moments that matter deserve more than ordinary glassware.<br/>We exist to celebrate freedom, heritage, and the spirit of America through thoughtfully crafted drinkware inspired by the values that bring people together.Our collection was created to honor the 250th anniversary of the United States — a tribute to the courage, pride, and traditions that shaped a nation. From backyard gatherings and family celebrations to raising a glass with friends, every piece is designed to turn everyday moments into meaningful memories.</p><p>We combine premium craftsmanship with bold patriotic designs to create glassware that feels personal, timeless, and made to be shared. Whether you're commemorating history, gifting someone special, or building your own collection, our goal is simple:</p><p>To create products that people are proud to hold, display, gift, and remember.</p><p>Because great stories deserve a great glass.</p>"
          }
        },
        "button_nEN3Q6": {
